          <p>Each day, we feature a different photograph of our universe, accompanied by a detailed explanation of its significance and context.</p>
          <p>From distant galaxies and nebulae to planets, moons, and space missions â€” Cosmos Daily helps you explore the cosmos one day at a time.</p>

          <form action="/apod/info" method="post" class="mt-5">
